content: As others have said, just consists of a very basic flowchart. Waste of money & time

Not sure why this costs money. It is just an interactive flow chart of things to ask yourself before you eat. I thought I would be able to record my responses so I could see trends over time but it does NOT do that.
Great in concept...needs some fixes to be a 5 star.  There is no setting for me to tell it to not ask me to check in during sleeping hours, and the remove alerts button is not working!
replyContent: Thanks for pointing this out! We've fixed the remove alerts button and it's now working as expected in this update.
